  <title>Cogl.TexturePixmapX11.new</title>
  <synopsis><code mime="text/x-gjs">
function new(context: <link xref="Cogl.Context">Cogl.Context</link>, pixmap: Number(guint32), automatic_updates: <link xref="Cogl.Bool">Cogl.Bool</link>): <link xref="Cogl.TexturePixmapX11">Cogl.TexturePixmapX11</link> {
    // Gjs wrapper for cogl_texture_pixmap_x11_new()
}
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Creates a texture that contains the contents of <code>pixmap</code>. If
<code>automatic_updates</code> is <code>true</code> then Cogl will attempt to listen for
damage events on the pixmap and automatically update the texture
when it changes.</p>
  <p>Since 1.10</p>
